    <note>Zhao(1) Zhi [20701] His three patrilineal ancestors all held office; his great grandfather being the first Xinan Zhao(1) listed in the Tang great minister genealogies. Zhi ended his career as Lingnan jiedu shi. XTS, 73B.16b-17b; Renming Da cidian, p. 1412. See also documentation for Song descendant, Bian [375]. Fengtian (modern Qianxian) county was on the Sichuan border and during the Song was frequently attached to Lizhou prefecture in Lizhou circuit.</note>
